{"tid":730843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國布吉觀光船沉沒 官員：49人失蹤 大部份是中國人","createTime":"2018-07-05T17:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T02:47:46.000Z","uid":36494,"like":191,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"136f8f824a2c57a74c4caae857f23afc2707d3c8","tid":730843,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180705&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58405287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180705%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58405287&d=uOklBcEPVMBt4WtBUitnIJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ec497a6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180705%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58405287&h=dc5adbe5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180705&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58405287</a><br />\n<br />\n【國際突發】泰國布吉觀光船沉沒 官員：49人失蹤<br />\n<br />\n泰國傳媒報道，泰國布吉兩艘觀光船周四因天氣惡劣關係沉沒，兩艘船共載有超過130名乘客。布吉府首長表示，至今仍有49人失蹤，事件中共有10人受傷，其中一人傷勢嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方表示，其中一艘觀光船下午5時許在布吉珊瑚島附近沉沒，船上載有97人，他們大部分都是中國人，布吉府首長表示，船上至今仍有49人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n另一艘載有39名中國及歐洲遊客的觀光船，其後則在神木島（Koh Maiton）附近沉沒，他們全部獲救返回岸上。從網上的圖片可見，途經出事船隻水域的漁船亦有加入救援。"},{"pid":"cb6f8bd5269b1603f500567d44f5f7fe5d4f213c","tid":730843,"uid":132587,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/184142_116e4ab2cc9bd5df406a214afa33b89f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F184142_116e4ab2cc9bd5df406a214afa33b89f.png&h=2bbf5cd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3991f69d937b4780edd669471afc5aed3d610082","tid":730843,"uid":166474,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"支那人冇一個係無辜ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e26acb68d5bffaad093fd5e2c7f2cb2dc8a7d42","tid":730843,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62f9625b46e296ee1d3085ca649ddc52d6a67d7f","tid":730843,"uid":61882,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:31:02.000Z","msg":"全泰國最精英嗰班潛水員去晒救班o靚仔<br />\n啲支那人就唯有浸住咸水先<br />\n等佢地得閒先撈番上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f582758fd39e06dab08a1b97f8e0482649ce52","tid":730843,"uid":104699,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"死咁少，不過都係一件美事"},{"pid":"0bd490eab3ef89ce9ab8970bf4a5e9d0397c4b4a","tid":730843,"uid":192263,"like":4,"dislike":68,"score":-64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:32:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02157de0477712ee441d4f99896468870fff3b39","tid":730843,"uid":80503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb6f8bd5269b1603f500567d44f5f7fe5d4f213c","tid":730843,"uid":132587,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/184142_116e4ab2cc9bd5df406a214afa33b89f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F184142_116e4ab2cc9bd5df406a214afa33b89f.png&h=2bbf5cd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32c5389f40fb7b5cbb4d4df1528c0f3f447a57f","tid":730843,"uid":34334,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11b992073ad08e21f15cccd8f68d356dd884af8b","tid":730843,"uid":81113,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"qu