s=\"hkgmoji\" />  全世界最top既救援人員去曬救果13個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  贏國可以名正言順去泰國救人 不過淨係去汁返果49件同胞 另外果邊唔洗你地幫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d72ebe6a01fd96dfc1566d653680b2d790dc75b","tid":730843,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T23:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出左新聞，有其他船救左</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救條撚咩，救既係另一條船！！！快D叫你老細又試喜迎抽死人水白事當紅事做啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F881903.com&d=uOklBcEPVMBt4WtBUitnIJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=440075f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">881903.com</a>：<br />\n<br />\n入境處未有接獲布吉觀光船意外港人求助<br />\n<br />\n06.07.2018 05:14<br />\n<br />\n泰國度假勝地布吉昨日傍晚出現暴風雨天氣，1艘載有中國遊客的觀光船隻翻沉，當地官員說，發現1具遊客屍體，仍有53名遊客失蹤。官員指，死者是1名男子，身上穿著救生衣。另1艘載39名中國及歐洲遊客的船隻亦都翻沉，所有人獲救送上岸。布吉政府深夜表示，搜救行動暫停。天氣預測顯示，當地惡劣天氣將維持到下周二。<br />\n<br />\n本港入境處表示，已透過外交部駐港特派員公署及中國駐普吉領事辦公室了解情況，至今未接獲港人求助，會繼續留意事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d52062b464ca4ed412872f7fa4350f2a59e3778e","tid":730843,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T23:25:14.000Z","msg":"中國或成為最大贏家"},{"pid":"a55d410ebdad10814b11b44a564f6d8100ad6473","tid":730843,"uid":23993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T23:26:46.000Z","msg":"0負皮 代表咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f69f0504bdf917abd6ab715ac369768162683eb","tid":730843,"uid":833,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a55d410ebdad10814b11b44a564f6d8100ad6473","tid":730843,"uid":23993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T23:26:46.000Z","msg":"0負皮 代表咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T23:28:41.000Z","msg":"五毛未開工"}]}